# 🚀 E-commerce Analytics Dashboard

## 🔍 Overview
An advanced data analytics dashboard built using Streamlit and Python to analyze e-commerce sales data.

## 💡 Features
- 📊 Interactive KPI Dashboard
- 📅 Date Range Filtering
- 🎯 Customer Segmentation
- 📈 Sales vs Profit Analysis
- 📦 Top Products Insights
- 🌍 Region-wise Analysis
- 📥 Data Export Feature

## 🛠 Tech Stack
- Python
- Pandas
- Streamlit
- Plotly

## 🚀 Live Demo
[Click Here](https://ecommercesales-dashboard.streamlit.app/)

## ⚙️ Run Locally
pip install -r requirements.txt  
streamlit run app.py